 - Tell me what's going on. - He is my father... 

00:01:45.520 --> 00:01:48.040
 ... I have to trust him. - It's a homicide. 

00:01:48.040 --> 00:01:51.330
 ... I know you went and took him. 

00:01:51.330 --> 00:01:55.619
 The longer the time goes, the more lies are said. 

00:01:55.619 --> 00:01:58.979
 - Do you want to let our investors go bankrupt? - You were lying. 

