 Let's go bankrupt. 

00:02:01.380 --> 00:02:02.490
 Police want to talk to me .. 

00:02:02.490 --> 00:02:04.740
 and I will not lie about you. 

00:02:04.740 --> 00:02:05.660
 The one who did it .. 

00:02:05.660 --> 00:02:09.779
 will not escape! 

00:02:09.779 --> 00:02:13.659
 - I'm your partner. - You are not my partner, you work for me! 

00:02:13.659 --> 00:02:17.649
 - You brought it to us. - That's what I do for us, for this family. 

00:02:17.649 --> 00:02:19.269
 Now do you tell me how to work? 

00:02:19.269 --> 00:02:20.619
 It's not your job, it's our life. 

